data.description: **Seller is offering buyer concessions!! This rancher plan features 11' x 10' covered back patio and laundry/mudroom off the garage. Cathedral ceilings and open floor concept run through the family room, dining room and the kitchen.  Kitchen features 42'' upper cabinets, an island with an eating bar overhang,stainless steel appliances, and a large walk-in pantry.  The master suite features a walk-in closet, and full bathroom with double sinks, garden tub, and 5' fiberglass shower. Full guest bathroom between guest bedrooms.
